OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy bill support plea   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffrom brewers and pubs      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pubs and brewery bosses have written to
OL,6, the government to ask for support with 
OL,7, their towering energy bills this       
OL,8, winter.                                
OL,10,FBosses of six of the UK's largest      
OL,11,Fbreweries and pubs said soaring costs  
OL,12,Fwould result in closures and "real and 
OL,13,Fserious irreversible" damage.          
OL,15,FUnlike households, firms aren't covered
OL,16,Fby a regulated energy price cap.       
OL,18,FThis means there is no protection from 
OL,19,Fsuppliers charging the maximum amount  
OL,20,Fper unit of energy.                    
